summary: ViewYahoo Website is about to Shut Down
title: ViewYahoo Website is about to Shut Down
body: At the end of the month ViewYahoo will be decommissioned at the end of the month. So you won’t be able to watch anime, tv shows or movies anymore. There’s also a lot of anime exclusive to there from Funimation, Sentai and Viz. So this may be the last time to see shows like K-on! and Princess Tutu for free.

title: You're Mine (Forever)
description:
by KTG

Kirishima Eijirou has been living with his best friend since high school, and he has enjoyed every minute of it! Bakugou is so manly and awesome, and he’s just so happy to spend his extra time with his best friend.

The thing is, Eijirou is getting more and more obsessed with Bakugou. At first, he just dismisses it as part of his lingering school-boy crush, but after he buys a bunch of devices used to help heroes catch villains, he realizes that he could actually capture someone else–someone Eijirou has wanted for a long, long time.

Now, it’s all just a matter of setting his plan into action.

PLEASE read the tags before delving into this fic; it has dark!Kirishima elements and explores Stockholm syndrome.
